casebody.data:
Roderick NUNLEY, petitioner,
v.
Cindy GRIFFITH, Warden. No. 15-5808 (15A247). Supreme Court of the United States Sept. 1, 2015.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Missouri denied.
